From a213ae67cb0e5f30a1ba34f09fbb804a5402bbf6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arun Vikas T <vikast@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 26 Sep 2025 16:08:45 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:HOSTAPD: Add SCS debugs in protocol and
 database code

Add SCS debugs in protocol parsing/processing code part and
database maintenance to improve debuggability of SCS
feature.

Patch-dependency:
r85-03-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-QM-NL80211-request-and-response.patch
r92-03-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-Add-SCS-data-structs-and-sta-info-fields.patch
r92-04-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-Add-support-for-SCS-req-parsing.patch
r92-05-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-Copy-and-send-SCS-data-over-QM.patch
r92-06-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-Handle-SCS-response-from-driver.patch
r92-07-UPSTREAM-PROTOCOL-CP-HOSTAPD-Add-support-for-sending-SCS-response.patch

Tag: SCS

Signed-off-by: Arun Vikas T <vikast@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 src/ap/robust_av.c           | 197 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
 src/drivers/driver_nl80211.c |  11 ++
 2 files changed, 190 insertions(+), 18 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/ap/robust_av.c b/src/ap/robust_av.c
